{"tid":2055943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"星島日報：網民號召明傍晚6時半港島遊行 紀念6月9日遊行一周年","createTime":"2020-06-08T10:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T11:45:38.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5ad64773e859fbaf8866c90d81107a231a7ef440","tid":2055943,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T10:36:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/網民號召明傍晚6時半港島遊行-紀念6月9日遊行-周年-064200027.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E8%99%9F%E5%8F%AC%E6%98%8E%E5%82%8D%E6%99%9A6%E6%99%82%E5%8D%8A%E6%B8%AF%E5%B3%B6%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B56%E6%9C%889%E6%97%A5%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-064200027.html&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=0bec6b95\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/網民號召明傍晚6時半港島遊行-紀念6月9日遊行-周年-064200027.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mST8O37yJfYdgUIDOo9S6Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200608a145320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FmST8O37yJfYdgUIDOo9S6Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200608a145320.jpg&h=01058bae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】反修例及反對國安法示威不斷，明日是6月9日民陣反對《逃犯條例》修訂大遊行發生一周年，有網民再度發起明日傍晚在「香港人抗爭一周年港島區大遊行」。<br />\n<br />\n網民號召集合時間為傍晚6時半，又預告明日下午5時半公佈哪一區集合，傍晚6時公布詳細集合地點，6時半公布示威路綫。網民又號召參加者以「彩虹衫」到場，因應情況換黑衫。惟行動未獲警方不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n去年6月9日民陣發起反對《逃犯條例》修訂大遊行，主辦單位宣稱有103萬人上街，多個港鐵站水泄不通，規模創回歸後新高，而警方稱，遊行人士最高峰有24萬人。"},{"pid":"c444176dfb3c282184ac9138d1922b335aa8da31","tid":2055943,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T10:37:42.000Z","msg":"金鐘 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670165aab5504565fc0d25c6da6c4559a7597825","tid":2055943,"uid":78184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T10:55:53.000Z","msg":"點解我唔知"},{"pid":"55b026aece32f153393e408c952b40c896594e94","tid":2055943,"uid":171849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T10:57:30.000Z","msg":"點解我唔知"},{"pid":"35d38ece8e565daf9bfccf418929e4f2511304e0","tid":2055943,"uid":277339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T11:01:02.000Z","msg":"又搞埋d黃絲都唔知既活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534cc32f4b007ff68536fb02f34ed4793bc2884d","tid":2055943,"uid":3357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T11:10:33.000Z","msg":"點解我唔知"},{"pid":"70190f3dbd1637f393212622796d25d006ee693b","tid":2055943,"uid":13308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T11:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}